      • setType

        public FacetConfiguration.FacetConfig setType​(String type)
        Optional type that relates to the available FacetCreators. If not set, it uses the default type of the related field. From some field-types different facet types can be generated:
        • numeric fields generate "interval" facets per default, but can be set to "range"
        • TODO: custom facet creators can support their own facet types
        Parameters:
        type -
        Returns:
        self
